          'By leveraging decentralized smart contracts, Boom Smart Shops enable instant, fee-light transactions. This means no heavy intermediaries or confusing fees—just the freedom to accept everyday payments in Bitcoin and beyond, all powered by the PayFi model.',
      },
    ]}
